proaches zero. The fundamental\nfeatures, which involve critical values of the classical and quantum field\nparameters, are discussed for the occurrence of the superradiance phase in this\nlimit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Dec 2020 17:40:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Mar 2021 18:27:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 8 Aug 2021 07:56:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-10"}
